data.title: Gustav, Prince of Vasa
data.meta_description: Prince Gustav of Vasa, Count of Itterburg, born Crown Prince of Sweden, was the son of King Gustav IV Adolf of Sweden and Queen Frederica. His Austrian princely title was actually spelled Wasa.
